title: Insights into metabolic disease
content: This episode of The Qualys discusses the manifestation of metabolic disease in a patient population predisposed to metabolic syndrome. The conversation covers the importance of early detection and intervention, as well as the role of lifestyle factors in the development of metabolic disease.

title: Theories on insulin resistance
content: The episode also delves into theories on the origins and evolutionary reasons for insulin resistance, which is a key factor in the development of metabolic disease. The discussion covers the potential role of diet, exercise, and other lifestyle factors in the development of insulin resistance.
